Vim
====
scroll windows

    :set scrollbind     # scb, set in window 1
    :set scrollbind     # scb, set in window 2

compare open windows

    :diffthis           # difft, in window 1
    :diffthis           # in window 2
    :diffoff            # diffo

    :diffs file_to_compare
    :vert diffs file_to_compare
